---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Typewriter from "astro-typewriter";
---

<div
    id="preface"
    class="p-7 md:mx-auto md:py-0 lg:p-10 md:h-screen md:snap-center md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center md:gap-[7vh] lg:gap-10 xl:p-30 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-rows-1 lg:justify-between lg:items-center md:portrait:flex md:portrait:flex-col md:portrait:justify-center md:portrait:gap-[5vh] lg:portrait:gap-[10vh] md:portrait:items-start md:portrait:p-20"
>
    <div
        id="toggle-preface-language"
        class="absolute top-1 right-13 md:top-5 md:right-17 prevent-select cursor-pointer bg-black text-white p-0.5 font-bold"
    >
        日本語
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-none items-center justify-start md:hidden">
        <h2 class="en-preface mb-3 text-center prevent-select">INTRODUCTION</h2>
        <h2 class="jp-preface hidden mb-3 text-center prevent-select">
            改まる
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div
        class="md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-between md:items-start gap-y-10 hidden"
    >
        <Typewriter
            class="md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-semibold"
            messages={[`Komes Pispol`, "中井イリア"]}
            writeSpeed={250}
            deleteSpeed={250}
            waitWritten={5000}
            waitDeleted={0}
        />
        <p class="en-preface md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
            An Aspiring CS student with strong foundation.
        </p>
        <p class="jp-preface hidden md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
            基礎を持って、CSを目指している学生。
        </p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <div
            class="en-preface mt-4 ml-2 mr-1 md:m-0 md:text-base/6 xl:text-base/8 2xl:text-base/10 md:portrait:text-base/10 lg:portrait:text-base/12"
            data-aos="fade-left"
            data-aos-duration="3000"
            data-aos-mirror="true"
        >
            <p class="text-4xl md:inline font-bold hidden">
                "It all occurred to me when I was 16 years old.
            </p>
            <p class="inline md:hidden">
                It all occurred to me when I was 16 years old.
            </p>
            <p>
                Having chosen an “Introduction to Web Programming” class, I came
                into a realization that art of programming is not out of my
                reach. From there I continued to explore various topics, from
                scripting languages like Python, to low level languages such as
                C and Rust. I could not and still cannot imagine any other
                fields I can enjoy other than the field of Computer Science.
                After high school graduation, I took a gap year to learn about
                the outside of Thailand. I went to Curtin College in Perth,
                Australia to study Diploma of Information and Technology
                (Computer Science), where I faced multiple challenges and
                learned from them. As I have completed my diploma, I have been
                continuously learning new topics, such as Cybersecurity and Game
                Development. All of this is to show that, I, indeed, take this
                path of Computer Science seriously. For now I look forward to
                studying at School of Information and Technology (SIT) at King
                Mongkut's University of Technology Thonburi (KMUTT) where I
                originally intended to attend."
            </p>
            <footer class="mt-10 md:hidden">- <cite>唯イズミ</cite></footer>
        </div>
        <div
            class="jp-preface mt-4 ml-2 mr-1 md:m-0 md:text-base/10 hidden"
            data-aos="fade-left"
            data-aos-duration="3000"
            data-aos-mirror="true"
        >
            <p class="text-4xl md:inline font-bold hidden">「日本語の内容</p>
            <p class="inline md:hidden">「日本語の内容</p>
            <p>まだ書いていません。日本語はまだ上手ではありませんので。」</p>
            <footer class="mt-10 md:hidden">- <cite>唯イズミ</cite></footer>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    import { toggleLanguage } from "../../public/scripts/language.js";

    toggleLanguage("toggle-preface-language", "jp-preface", "en-preface");
</script>
